  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTg4MTZkZTJhNzFhYWI1YmU2NWNiLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yNDYmaGVpZ2h0PTQxMg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/58816de2a71aab5be65cb.jpg?width=246&amp;height=412\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/58816de2a71aab5be65cb.jpg?width=246&amp;height=412\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/58816de2a71aab5be65cb.jpg?width=246&amp;height=412\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Mikhailovich,_Count_Brasov<br/>\n<br/>\r\n罗曼诺夫家族直系里最后一个男性后代，皇位的继承人，<br/>\r\n这位祖母死后拿到一大笔遗产，在法国买了辆克莱斯勒跑车（已经无法考证是哪一款了，所以有两个可能）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzcyMTM1MGY0YzcxNThiOWQ3ZTFjLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNTg3JmhlaWdodD04OTI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3721350f4c7158b9d7e1c.jpg?width=1587&amp;height=892\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3721350f4c7158b9d7e1c.jpg?width=1587&amp;height=892\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3721350f4c7158b9d7e1c.jpg?width=1587&amp;height=892\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmUwNzkyMTU5MDIxYmU1MmViY2FmLmpwZz93aWR0aD03MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTQwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fe0792159021be52ebcaf.jpg?width=700&amp;height=400\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fe0792159021be52ebcaf.jpg?width=700&amp;height=400\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fe0792159021be52ebcaf.jpg?width=700&amp;height=400\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n夏天期末考试后和好朋友出去兜风，都撞死了<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n苏联，俄罗斯一代名车，全苏联人社会地位的象征，权力和社会成功的代表，伏尔加牌轿车，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjgwMjJiNDcxNDFkMTA1ZDg0ODJiLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDI0JmhlaWdodD03Njg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/28022b47141d105d8482b.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=768\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/28022b47141d105d8482b.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=768\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/28022b47141d105d8482b.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=768\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n在成功引进美国先进技术，员工专门去美国培训，生产线完全按照美国的场地，规格，样式建造后，以克莱斯勒为基础生产的新一代伏尔加牌轿车，<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTI5MGE2OTkyY2ViZjUwN2Q5NGFhLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNjAwJmhlaWdodD0xMTIz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5290a6992cebf507d94aa.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=1123\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5290a6992cebf507d94aa.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=1123\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5290a6992cebf507d94aa.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=1123\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGQ5ODZiYWQxMTM0OTFkNTc5ZmQ1LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMzAwJmhlaWdodD0xMDU0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd986bad113491d579fd5.jpg?width=1300&amp;height=1054\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd986bad113491d579fd5.jpg?width=1300&amp;height=1054\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd986bad113491d579fd5.jpg?width=1300&amp;height=1054\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n总统亲自出席下线仪式，<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMmNjNmVmNGZiNGJjNjhkNjRjZWE2LmpwZz93aWR0aD04NjEmaGVpZ2h0PTEzOTA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2cc6ef4fb4bc68d64cea6.jpg?width=861&amp;height=1390\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2cc6ef4fb4bc68d64cea6.jpg?width=861&amp;height=1390\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2cc6ef4fb4bc68d64cea6.jpg?width=861&amp;height=1390\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGQxZGY1ODBmYTRkMTYyM2IyYzc1LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjAwJmhlaWdodD02MzA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd1df580fa4d1623b2c75.jpg?width=1200&amp;height=630\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd1df580fa4d1623b2c75.jpg?width=1200&amp;height=630\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd1df580fa4d1623b2c75.jpg?width=1200&amp;height=630\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n刚投产就遇到金融危机，卖得一塌糊涂堪比智障，很快就停产<br/>\r\n伏尔加Siber的原型车，克莱斯勒赛百灵<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMmRmNTk5YzAxZTUxMDNmNjQ0ZDAyLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDI0JmhlaWdodD03Njg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2df599c01e5103f644d02.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=768\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2df599c01e5103f644d02.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=768\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2df599c01e5103f644d02.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=768\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
